Rich Dad Poor Dad

Passion is anger and love combined.
It's feare that keeps most people working at a job: the fear of not paying their bills, the fear of being fired, the fear of not having enough money, 
and the fear of starting over.
He understood that every person has a weak and needy part of their soul that can be bought, and he knew that every individual also had a part of their 
soul that was resilient and could never be bought.
